Carolco Pictures Inc said it signeda letter of intent to exchange 2.2 mln of its shares for allOrbis Communications Inc stock within the next 60 days.    It said the Carolco shares used in the exchange are valuedat 7.00 dlrs a share or a total value of 15.4 mln dlrs and willbe adjusted based on the price of Carolco shares on the closingdate.    It said Orbis management will remain in place for at leastthree years. Reuter&#3;